At Cannes - a stage for stories, for spirit, for self-expression 
I walked in not just wearing a dress, but wearing my brand, my journey and every strand of representation that @nishhair stands for

**“I’m Sonali — the woman behind Sonansh.
No big team, no fancy setup, not even a first sale yet.
Just one girl with a dream, designing every piece with love and building this from scratch.

It’s not a full business yet, but it’s fully mine.
And this is just the beginning.”**

And this song in the background? It touched my soul.
@nishhair @gulati06 — thank you for being a light for so many of us.
Truly, an inspiration for every girl with a small dream and big heart.”**
